Cell[BoxData["\<\"famB is valid basis. The definitions of the basis will be \
saved in \\\"famB\\\" directory.\\n    Ds[famB] \[LongDash] denominators,\\n  \
  SPs[famB] \[LongDash] scalar products involving loop momenta,\\n    \
LMs[famB] \[LongDash] loop momenta,\\n    EMs[famB] \[LongDash] external \
momenta,\\n    Parameters[famB] \[LongDash] parameters (invariants, masses, \
dimension),\\n    Toj[famB] \[LongDash] rules to transform scalar products to \
denominators,\\n    CutDs[famB] \[LongDash] flag vector of cut \
denominators.\"\>"], "Print",
