Cell[BoxData["\<\"Found 1543 mapped sectors and 5068 unique sectors.\\n    \
UniqueSectors[famB] \[LongDash] unique sectors.\\n    MappedSectors[famB] \
\[LongDash] mapped sectors.\\n    SR[famB][\[Ellipsis]] \[LongDash] symmetry \
relations for j[famB,\[Ellipsis]] from UniqueSectors[famB].\\n    \
jSymmetries[famB,\[Ellipsis]] \[LongDash] symmetry rules for the sector \
js[famB,\[Ellipsis]] in UniqueSectors[famB].\\n    jRules[famB,\[Ellipsis]] \
\[LongDash] reduction rules for j[famB,\[Ellipsis]] from MappedSectors[famB].\
\\n    SectorsMappings[famB] gives the list of mappings of all sectors from \
MappedSectors[famB] to UniqueSectors[famB].\"\>"], "Print",
